Fresh Pi session: UPDATE THE CANON TDD TEST LIST.

Inputs:
- Test-list history under {{run.dir}}/test-list/
- Latest selected scenario under {{run.dir}}/tdd/
- Latest green/refactor verification under {{run.dir}}/tdd/
- All discovered-scenarios-*.json not already incorporated
- Worktree: {{run.worktree-dir}}

Goal:
Create the next immutable test-list snapshot after a verified green increment.

Rules:
- Do not edit repository files.
- Start from the newest valid test-list snapshot, or the initial list.
- Mark exactly the selected scenario `complete` and retain its id.
- Append genuinely new discoveries as `pending` with new stable ids; deduplicate behavior already represented.
- Preserve all other scenario states and scope.
- Record evidence linking the completed scenario to its concrete test.
- Return `actions_needed` if pending scenarios remain, otherwise `no_actions`.

Write:
- JSON snapshot: {{run.dir}}/test-list/scenarios-{{run.round}}.json
- Markdown snapshot: {{run.dir}}/test-list/scenarios-{{run.round}}.md
- Status: {{run.dir}}/test-list/update-status-{{run.round}}.json

Status examples:
{"status":"actions_needed","summary":"pending scenarios remain","issues_file":null}
{"status":"no_actions","summary":"test list is empty","issues_file":null}
{"status":"fail","summary":"test list could not be updated safely","issues_file":null}
